snippet.title: HawkZombie Plays: Nightmare Traveler
snippet.description:
A short (and I do mean short) horror game our dear friend to the channel, Kato, developed for a few Game Jams going on this month. It's creepy, and was a lot of fun to play. Good luck, Kato!

https://kato-san.itch.io/nightmare-traveler

Originally broadcast on https://twitch.tv/hawkzombie 
Interested in helping support more videos like this one? https://www.patreon.com/hawkzombie

Goofy, irreverent commentary & voices during game play, moderate swearing, and adult innuendo/references.

Intro/Outro background originally done by https://www.facebook.com/tomgillingham2d3danimator
Intro/Outro Music - "Miami Nights - Extended Theme" Kevin MacLeod (incompetech.com)
